  {
    "page_number": 1,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      82.79,
      544.22,
      194.93
    ],
    "text": "The National Operation \u201cCountry Together\u201d has been in operation since 30.10.2025 with the objective of comprehensively combating drug-related crime across the country through a multi-pronged strategy. The operation focuses on disrupting the supply of illicit drugs nationwide, reducing the demand for narcotics, intensifying enforcement operations, rehabilitating individuals affected by drug addiction, implementing preventive awareness programs to discourage drug abuse, and strengthening community participation in the fight against drugs.",
    "fonts": [
      "TimesNewRomanPS-BoldMT",
